name: dart_fusion_flutter
desc: A library that brings together a harmonious blend of essential tools, utilities, and components designed to supercharge your Dart projects.

name: AssetRunner
desc: Runner to scan asset and turn it into one model class.

name: AssetRunner
desc: Default constant constructor with input is assets and output is lib/src/assets.dart.

name: arguments
desc: Gets the arguments for the runner as a list of strings.

name: AssetRunner.help
desc: Printing usage information of AssetRunner.

name: input
desc: Input directory of where the asset is. By default is assets.

name: name
desc: The name of the runner.

name: output
desc: Output file of where the generated model should take place. By default is lib/src/assets.dart.

name: DBehavior
desc: A custom scroll behavior for controlling the scrolling physics of scrollable widgets.

name: DBehavior
desc: Creates a DBehavior instance with optional custom ScrollPhysics.

name: getScrollPhysics
desc: The scroll physics to use for the platform given by getPlatform.

name: physics
desc: The custom ScrollPhysics instance to be used for scrolling.

name: DBuilder
desc: A widget that builds its child using a custom builder function with optional data.

name: DBuilder
desc: Creates an DBuilder widget with the specified builder function and optional data.

name: build
desc: Describes the part of the user interface represented by this widget.

name: builder
desc: The function that builds the child widget using the BuildContext and JSON data.

name: data
desc: The optional JSON data that can be passed to the builder function.

name: DButton
desc:
A custom button widget that wraps the InkMaterial widget to provide
tap interactions with various customization options.

name: DButton
desc: Creates a custom button widget with optional parameters for customization.

name: borderRadius
desc: The rounded corners of the button.

name: build
desc: Describes the part of the user interface represented by this widget.

name: child
desc: An optional custom child widget for the button.

name: color
desc: The background color of the button.

name: controller
desc: The controller to manually control the interaction states of the material.

name: decoration
desc: Custom decoration for button.

name: decorationPosition
desc: Decoration Position by default on background

name: focusColor
desc: The color when the material is focused.

name: gap
desc: The space between the text and prefix/suffix widgets.

name: highlightColor
desc: The color when the material is highlighted.

name: hoverColor
desc: The color when the material is hovered.

name: ignore
desc: Determines whether the button should ignore tap interactions.

name: mainAxisSize
desc: The main axis size of the button.

name: margin
desc: The margin around the button.

name: onTap
desc: The callback function triggered when the button is tapped.

name: padding
desc: The padding around the button content.

name: prefix
desc: An optional widget to display before the text.

name: shapeBorder
desc: The custom shape of the material.

name: splashColor
desc: The color when the material is splashed.

name: style
desc: The text style for the button text.

name: suffix
desc: An optional widget to display after the text.

name: text
desc: The text to display inside the button.

name: textAlign
desc: Alignment for DButton.text.

name: DChangeBuilder
desc:
A widget that listens to changes in a ChangeNotifier and rebuilds its
child widgets based on the changes.

name: DChangeBuilder
desc: Creates a DChangeBuilder widget.

name: build
desc: Describes the part of the user interface represented by this widget.

name: builder
desc: The builder function that provides the updated value and an optional child.

name: child
desc: An optional child widget to include within the rebuilt widget.

name: value
desc: The instance of ChangeNotifier to listen to for changes.

name: DImage
desc: A widget for displaying vector or bitmap images from different sources.

name: DImage
desc: Creates an DImage widget with the specified source.

name: alignment
desc: The alignment of the image within its container.

name: build
desc: Describes the part of the user interface represented by this widget.

name: color
desc: A color filter to apply to the image.

name: colorBlendMode
desc: The blending mode to apply to the color.

name: copyWith
desc: Creates a copy of this DImage but with the given fields replaced with the new values.

name: errorBuilder
desc: A builder function to create a widget when the image fails to load.

name: fit
desc: How the image should be inscribed into the space allocated for it.

name: placeholderBuilder
desc: A builder function to create a placeholder widget while the image is being loaded.

name: semanticsLabel
desc: A description of the image for accessibility purposes.

name: size
desc: The desired size of the image.

name: source
desc: The source of the image to be displayed.

name: DInherited
desc: A scope to pass DState data to its descendant.

name: DInherited
desc: Default constructor to pass DState to its descendant.

name: of
desc: A shortcut to call DInherited from BuildContext.

name: updateShouldNotify
desc: Whether the framework should notify widgets that inherit from this widget.

name: value
desc: DState data to be passed.

name: DLogWidget
desc: A widget that logs a message using DLog and then returns a child widget.

name: DLogWidget
desc: Creates a DLogWidget with the specified message, level, and child.

name: build
desc: Describes the part of the user interface represented by this widget.

name: child
desc: The child widget to return after logging the message.

name: level
desc: The log level, defaults to DLevel.info.

name: message
desc: The message to log.

name: onDebug
desc: Choose wether print log on debug or anytime.

name: DOverlay
desc: A builder widget that displays an overlay.

name: DOverlay
desc: Creates an instance of DOverlay.

name: builder
desc: The widget to be displayed within the overlay.

name: controller
desc: Controller of OverlayEntry.

name: duration
desc: Duration for how much long does the value changes taking.

name: onFinish
desc: Overriding DState.dispose inside createState.

name: onStart
desc: Overriding DState.build inside createState.

name: DOverlayController
desc: A custom overlay that displays a widget on top of other content.

name: DOverlayController
desc: Creates an DOverlay with the provided child.

name: builder
desc:
This entry will include the widget built by this builder in the overlay at
the entry's position.

name: child
desc: The widget to be displayed within the overlay.

name: display
desc: Displays the overlay.

name: dispose
desc: Discards any resources used by this OverlayEntry.

name: duration
desc: Duration for how much long does the value changes taking.

name: DProvider
desc: A generic InheritedWidget for providing a value of type T to its descendants.

name: DProvider
desc: Creates a DProvider.

name: of
desc: Retrieves the value of type T from the nearest ancestor DProvider.

name: updateShouldNotify
desc: Whether the framework should notify widgets that inherit from this widget.

name: value
desc: The value of type T that is provided to descendants.

name: DRunner
desc: The base abstract class for a DRunner.

name: DRunner
desc: Default constant constructor of DRunner with help as false.

name: arguments
desc: Gets the arguments for the runner as a list of strings.

name: DRunner.help
desc: Constant constructor for printing help.

name: help
desc: Choose wether to print help for this runner or not.

name: name
desc: The name of the runner.

name: run
desc: Runs the Dart process for the runner wether onDebug only or on every profile.

name: DState
desc: State child class of DWidget.

name: build
desc: Describes the part of the user interface represented by this widget.

name: data
desc: Declare DWidget.data.

name: dispose
desc: Called when this object is removed from the tree permanently.

name: initState
desc: Called when this object is inserted into the tree.

name: update
desc: Overriding setState.

name: DTextArea
desc: A custom text area widget.

name: DTextArea
desc: Creates a DTextArea.

name: backgroundColor
desc: Background color of the text area.

name: borderRadius
desc: The border radius of the text area.

name: borderSideActive
desc: Border side when the text area is active.

name: borderSideIdle
desc: Border side when the text area is idle.

name: build
desc: Describes the part of the user interface represented by this widget.

name: contentPadding
desc: Padding for the content inside the text area.

name: controller
desc: Controller for the text area.

name: cursorColor
desc: Color of the cursor in the text area.

name: decoration
desc: Decoration for the text field.

name: footer
desc: Footer widget to be displayed in the text area.

name: hintStyle
desc: Style for the hint text.

name: hintText
desc: Hint text to be displayed when the text area is empty.

name: isDense
desc: Whether the InputDecorator.child is part of a dense form (i.e., uses less vertical space).

name: labelStyle
desc: Style for the label text.

name: labelText
desc: Label text to be displayed in the text area.

name: margin
desc: Margin for the text area.

name: maxLines
desc: Maximum number of lines for the text area.

name: minLines
desc: Minimum number of lines for the text area.

name: onSubmitted
desc: Callback function when the text is submitted.

name: placeholder
desc: Placeholder widget to be displayed within the text area when it's empty.

name: prefixIcon
desc: Icon to be displayed at the beginning of the text area.

name: suffixIcon
desc: Icon to be displayed at the end of the text area.

name: textAlign
desc: Alignment of the text within the text area.

name: textStyle
desc: Style for the text in the text area.

name: DTileWrapper

desc: Creates a DTileWrapper with the specified builder function.

desc: The function that builds the ExpansionTile widget with customization.

name: createState
desc: Creates the mutable state for this widget at a given location in the tree.

name: DWidget
desc: Making StatefulWidget prettier and less boilerplate.

name: DWidget
desc: Default constant constructor with one field of key.

desc: Creates the mutable state for this widget at a given location in the tree.

name: data
desc: A map to declare and passing data inside class. This make things cleaner.

name: onFinish
desc: Overriding DState.dispose inside createState.

name: onPreparation
desc: Overriding DState.initState inside createState.

name: LocalizeRunner
desc: Runner to translate Locale and generate a model to be integrated with easy_localization.

name: LocalizeRunner
desc:
Default constant constructor where the input by default is assets/translation/en.json,
with default Locale
from en and targetting list of Locale in DartFusion.locales.

name: arguments
desc: Gets the arguments for the runner as a list of strings.

name: exclude
desc: List of excluded translation. By default its empty.

name: from
desc: Base Locale. By default is Locale('en').

name: LocalizeRunner.help
desc: Printing usage information of LocalizeRunner.

name: input
desc: Input json default localization file. By default is assets/translation/en.json.

name: name
desc: The name of the runner.

name: output
desc: Output generated model to be integrated with easy_localization.

name: to
desc: List of targeted translation. By default its DartFusion.locales.

name: translate
desc: Choose whether to translate json to targetted locales or not.

name: ModelRunner

desc: Gets the arguments for the runner as a list of strings.

name: ModelRunner.help
desc: Printing usage information of ModelRunner.

name: input
desc: Input directory of where the models in.

name: name
desc: The name of the runner.

name: OnContext
desc: A set of extension collection on BuildContext.

name: bottomTheme
desc: The BottomNavigationBarThemeData defined for the current ThemeData.

name: color
desc: The ColorScheme defined for the current ThemeData.

name: height
desc: The height of the media query for this BuildContext.

name: isDesktop
desc:
Returns true if the width of the media query for this BuildContext
is greater than 700.0, indicating it's a desktop-sized device.

name: isPhone
desc:
Returns true if the width of the media query for this BuildContext
is less than 400.0, indicating it's a phone-sized device.

name: isTablet
desc:
Returns true if the width of the media query for this BuildContext
is greater than 400.0 and less than 700.0, indicating it's a tablet-sized device.

name: provider
desc: A shortcut to call DProvider of context.

name: query
desc: The MediaQueryData for this BuildContext.

name: querySize
desc: The size of the media query for this BuildContext.

name: state
desc: Getting DState from its descendant.

name: text
desc: The TextTheme defined for the current ThemeData.

name: theme
desc: The ThemeData defined for this BuildContext.

name: value
desc: A shortcut to get DState.data with BuildContext.

name: width
desc: The width of the media query for this BuildContext.

name: OnDState
desc: Extensioning values used in DState.

name: value
desc: A shortcut to call value from DState.data.

Extension on ExpansionTile providing a convenient method to create a copy
